mmunication: Revised recommendations for cardiovascular monitoring and use of multiple sclerosis drug Gilenya (fingolimod). Available from: URL: http://www.fda.gov/Drugs/DrugSafety/ucm303192.htm#data." ([2012 May 14]):[5] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0', 1767363026);
